	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, like Subject says.
<br />After release of MOE0 I'v got a lot comments about grafics upgrade.I really tried to, but I myself can't produce any good grafics.
<br />Actually, about month ago I asked Dizzy series community(MOE is definitly Dizzy like game) about the same, and I got lot of "OK, why not" answers.
<br />MOE1 is progressing nicely and should be finished in december(25th?).
<br />SO why I'm writing this?
<br />Actually, originally I was planning to use Dizzy games grafics only.
<br />Oliver Twins(Fathers of Dizzy games series)gave OK for such things very long ago(as long as games made with their grafics are not sold).
<br />The problem now is that I run out of grafics from dizzy games.
<br />I asked few peoples to help me, but no one agreed.
<br />For example, I need Library grafics.Why not use Addams Family "Study Room" grafics?
<br />I'm not asking about legality thing.
<br />I'm asking how do you people feel about such...action(stealing grafics from other games).Do you condemn it? Or don't care about it?
<br />Feel free to call me a "bad guy", I don't mind it, really.
<br />Thanks for any comments on this.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


