	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't mind ripping graphics for non-commercial hobby projects. In fact I'm planning to do that for my own engine demo, because I have not been able to found a committed graphics artist.
<br />
<br />I agree with everything Shiru said though, it's surprisingly hard to rip graphics because of different styles and often very good graphics also have some kind of layering/shadowing/etc going on which takes some time to figure out if you want to apply it in to your own levels as well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


